OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly cloudy this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, with patchy outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain, mainly in the east, but these
OL,9,Fwill become more widespread towards
OL,10,Fdawn. Turning chilly where any cloud
OL,11,Fbreaks do occur, with a few fog
OL,12,Fpatches possible.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FA largely cloudy morning,
OL,15,Fwith some light rain in places,
OL,16,Fnotably in the east. The cloud may
OL,17,Fbreak during the afternoon to allow
OL,18,Fsome sunshine through. Feeling a
OL,19,Flittle milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
